Work with people
who care

You matter to us. At BlueGrid, we like to work with
your personal outlook. Keeping you and your goals
at the heart of your thought-process, we help you work
through your finances and manage your wealth in a
way that serves you best.

You first,
transaction second.

BlueGrid was founded solely with a view to serve people
in the true sense of the term. Our differentiator lies in our
customer-centricity. We grow when you grow with us.

Customer-Centric Process

Our customer-centricity flows into every step that we take to develop your ideal portfolio.
The steps in our approach towards serving you are highlighted herewith.

Phase 1

Assess

We begin by listening to you. We learn
about your objectives, your perspective
on risk, your expectations, your liquidity
need for the short term & long term,
and your money philosophies. The
assessment also involves creating your
risk profile to determine the optimal
level of risk you are willing to take.

Phase 2

Create

The next step is to create a blueprint on the
basis of our discussions and understanding
of you and your risk profile. Click here to
understand the factors we take into
consideration when creating your blueprint.

Phase 3

Implement

We put the created & discussed plan into
action by choosing investment vehicles
and services uniquely suited to your needs,
goals, and risk tolerance. We adopt the
latest technology to implement your
approved investment plan for convenience,
security of your funds, and transparency.

Phase 4

Review

As time passes, things change, and so do
market situations. We constantly review
your portfolio health, performance of your
investment portfolio, and ensure timely
alignment of changes in your plan to the
changes in your goals.
